	      1/2
	 /\(3)
	 |     2			  1/3
	 |    m qm pbf(3 * CV / 9) = ya (r   )
	 |
	\/ 1

Gur vagrteny bs m fdhnerq, qm
Sebz 1 gb gur fdhner ebbg bs 3
	Gvzrf gur pbfvar
	Bs 3 CV bire avar
Vf gur ybt bs gur phor ebbg bs r
%
	   (1/2)
	/ 3
	|       2         3 k 3.14            (1/2)
	|      m qm  pbf (--------)   =  ya(r     )
	/ 1		     9

Gur vagrteny, sebz bar gb ebbg guerr,
Bs m gb gur frpbaq qm,
	Gvzrf gur pbfvar
	Bs 3 cv bire avar
Vf gur ybt bs gur guveq ebbg bs r.
%
	12 + 144 + 20 + 3(4)                  2
	----------------------  +  5(11)  =  9  +  0
		  7

N qbmra, n tebff naq n fpber,
Cyhf guerr gvzrf gur fdhner ebbg bs sbhe,
	Qvivqrq ol frira,
	Cyhf svir gvzrf ryrira,
Rdhnyf avar fdhnerq cyhf mreb, ab zber!
%
N onq yvggyr tvey va Znqevq,
N zbfg ercerurafvoyr xvq,
	Gbyq ure Gnagr Ybhvfr
	Gung ure phag fzryyrq yvxr purrfr,
Naq gur jbefg bs vg jnf gung vg qvq!
%
N ongure jubfr pybguvat jnf fgerjrq
Ol oerrmrf gung yrsg ure dhvgr ahqr,
	Fnj n zna pbzr nybat
	Naq, hayrff V'z dhvgr jebat,
Lbh rkcrpgrq guvf yvar gb or yrjq.
%
N orng fpuvmbcueravp fnvq, "Zr?
V nz abg V, V'z n gerr."
	Ohg nabgure, zber fnar,
	Fubhgrq, "V'z n Terng Qnar!"
Naq pbirerq uvf cnagf yrt jvgu crr.
%
N ornhgvshy oryyr bs Qry Abegr
Vf erpxbarq qvfqnvashy naq unhtugl
	Orpnhfr qhevat gur qnl
	Fur fnlf: "Oblf, xrrc njnl!"
Ohg fur shpxf va gur tybnzvat yvxr sbegl.
%
N ornhgvshy ynql anzrq Cflpur
Vf ybirq ol n sryybj anzrq Vxrl.
	Bar guvat nobhg Vxr
	Gur ynql pna'g yvxr
Vf uvf cevpx, juvpu vf qernqshyyl fcvxrl.
%
N orrgyvat lbhat jbzna anzrq Cevqtrgf
Unq n ivbyrag noubeerapr bs zvqtrgf;
	Bss gur raq bs n junes
	Fur bapr chfurq n qjnes
Jubfr gehapngvba erqhprq ure gb svqtrgf.
		-- Rqjneq Tberl
%
N ovt-obfbzrq Ohaal anzrq Terffvba
Fbyq pvtnef ng n xrl-pyho pbaprffvba.
	Jura fur fjviryrq nobhg
	Rira fgebat zra pevrq bhg,
Sbe ure pbfghzr qvq abg xrrc ure syrfu va.
%
N ovfrkhny punc anzr bs Yhag
Gnhtug uvzfrys na hahfhny fghag.
Ur pbhyq crry onpx uvf fcbhg
Ghea gur fxva vafvqr bhg
Yvxr n tybir, gb or hfrq nf n phag!
%
N obool bs Abggvatunz Whapgvba
Jubfr betna unq ybat prnfrq gb shapgvba
	Qrprvirq uvf tbbq jvsr
	Sbe gur erfg bs ure yvsr
Jvgu gur nvq bs uvf pbafgnoyr'f gehapurba.
%
N oebxra-qbja uneybg anzrq Ghccf
Jnf urneq gb pbasrff va ure phcf:
	"Gur urvtug bs zl sbyyl
	Jnf shpxvat n pbyyvr --
Ohg V tbg n avpr cevpr sbe gur chcf."
%
N oheyrfdhr qnapre, n cvc
Anzrq Ivetvavn, pbhyq crry va n mvc;
	Ohg fur ernq fpvrapr svpgvba
	Naq qvrq bs pbafgevpgvba
Nggrzcgvat n Zbrovhf fgevc.
		-- Plevy Xbeaoyhgu, "Gur Hasbeghangr Gbcbybtl"
%
N ohfl lbhat ynql anzrq Tybevn
Jnf unq ol Fve Trenyq qh Znhevre
	Naq gura ol fvk zra,
	Fve Trenyq ntnva,
Naq gur onaq ng gur Jnyqbes-Nfgbevn.
%
N pnova obl ba na byq pyvccre
Terj fgrnqvyl syvccre naq syvccre.
	Ur cyhttrq hc uvf nff
	Jvgu sentzragf bs tynff
Naq guhf pvephzpvfrq uvf byq fxvccre.
%
N pnhgvbhf lbhat sryybj anzrq Ybqtr,
Unq frngorygf vafgnyyrq va uvf Qbqtr.
	Jvgu uvf qngr nyy fgenccrq va
	Ur pbzzvggrq n fva
Jvgubhg rira yrnivat gur tnentr.
		-- "N Obl naq Uvf Qbt"
%
N pnhgvbhf lbhat sryybj anzrq Ghaarl
Unq n junat gung jnf jbegu nal zbarl.
	Jura rnfrq va unys-jnl,
	Gur tvey'f fvtu znqr uvz fnl,
"Jul gur fvtu?"  "Sbe gur erfg bs vg, ubarl."
%
N pregnva lbhat zna, vg jnf abgrq,
Jrag nobhg va gur urng guvpxyl-pbngrq;
	Ur fnvq, "Lbh znl fpbss,
	Ohg V funa'g gnxr vg bss;
Haqrearngu V nz ubeevoyl oybngrq."
		-- Rqjneq Tberl
%
N pregnva lbhat crefba bs Turag,
Hapregnva vs ynql be trag,
	Fubjf uvf betnaf ng ynetr
	Sbe n fznyy unaqyvat punetr
Gb nffvfg uvz va cnlvat gur erag.
%
N pregnva lbhat furvx bs Nytvref
Fnvq gb uvf unerz, "Zl qrnef,
	Gubhtu lbh znl guvax vg bqq bs zr,
	V'z gverq bs whfg fbqbzl
Yrg'f gel fgenvtug shpxvat."  (ybhq purref!)
%
N punc qbja va Bxynubzn
Unq n pbpx gung pbhyq fvat Yn Cnybzn,
	Ohg gur fjrrgarff bs cvgpu
	Pbhyqa'g chg bss gur uvgpu
Bs vzcbgrapr, fvmr naq nebzn.
%
N punezre sebz byq Nznevyyb,
Fvpx bs svaqvat fgenatr urnqf ba ure cvyybj,
	Qrpvqrq bar qnl
	Gung gb xrrc zra njnl
Fur jbhyq fghss hc ure perivpr jvgu Oevyyb.
%
N puvccl jub jbexrq va Oynpx Oyhss
Unq n chffl nf ynetr nf n zhss.
	Vg unq ebbz sbe obgu unaqf
	Naq fbzr vagvzngr tynaqf,
Naq jnf fbsg nf n yvggyr qhpx'f syhss.
%
N pyretvpny fghqrag anzrq Fvzzf
Uhzf yvghetvpny gharf juvyr ur evzf:
	N avpr cvrpr bs nff
	Trgf gur O-Zvabe Znff ...
Nyy gur bguref trg Natyvpna ulzaf.
%
N pyrevpny fghqrag anzrq Celar
Guebhtu cnva fbhtug gb ernpu gur qvivar:
	Ur jber n unve fuveg,
	Dhvgr bsgra ngr qveg,
Naq ongurq rirel Sevqnl va oevar.
		-- Rqjneq Tberl
%
N pyrire lbhat zna anzrq Rhtrar
Vairagrq n wnpx-bss znpuvar.
	Ba gur gjragl-guveq fgebxr
	Gur shpxva' guvat oebxr
Naq orng obgu uvf onyyf gb n pernz.
%
N pbpxfhpxvat fgrab anzrq Orrzna
Erznexrq nf fur fjnyybjrq zl frzra :
	"Ba zl zvahfphyr fnynel
	 V zhfg jngpu rirel pnybevr,
Fb V trg `nurnq' rngvat lbh ur-zra!"
%
N pbzchgre pnyyrq Vyyvnp4
Unq n engure gbhtu oht va vgf pber.
	Vg purjrq hc vgf pneqf
	Naq fcrjrq lneqf naq lneqf
Bs vyyrtvoyr gncr ba gur sybbe.
%
N pbzchgre, gb cevag bhg n snpg,
Jvyy qvivqr, zhygvcyl, naq fhogenpg.
	Ohg guvf bhgchg pna or
	Ab zber guna qroevf,
Vs gur vachg jnf fubeg bs rknpg.
		-- Tvtb
%
N pbagbegvbavfg unvyvat sebz Ylapu
Hfrq gb erag bhg uvf gbby ol gur vapu.
	N sbbg pbfg n dhvq --
	Ur pbhyq naq ur qvq
Fgergpu vg gb guerr va n cvapu.
%
N pbechyrag znvqra anzrq Xebyy
Unq n abgvba rkprrqvatyl qebyy:
	Ng n znfdhrenqr onyy,
	Qerffrq va abguvat ng nyy,
Fur onpxrq va nf n Cnexre Ubhfr ebyy.
%
N pbhcyr jnf svfuvat arne Pybzor
Jura gur znvq ortna ybbxvat dhvgr tyhz,
	Naq fnvq, "Obgure gur svfu!
	V'q engure pbvfu!"
Juvpu gurl qvq -- juvpu jnf jul gurl unq pbzr.
%
N pbjunaq jnl bhg va Frnggyr
Unq n qbbsyvpxre syng nf n cnqqyr.
	Ur fnvq, "Ab, V pna'g shpx
	N ynzo be n qhpx,
Ohg tbyyl! vg whfg svgf gur pnggyr."
%
N pehfnqre'f jvsr fyvccrq sebz gur tneevfba
Naq unq na nssnve jvgu n Fnenpra.
	Fur jnf abg birefrkrq,
	Be wrnybhf be irkrq,
Fur whfg jnagrq gb znxr n pbzcnevfba.
%
N pehfnqre'f jvsr fyvccrq sebz gur tneevfba
Naq unq na nssnve jvgu n Fnenpra.
	Fur jnf abg birefrkrq,
	Be wrnybhf be irkrq,
Fur whfg jnagrq gb znxr n pbzcnevfba.
%
N PF fghqrag anzrq Yva
Unq n cevpx gur fvmr bs n cva
	Vg jnf ab tbbq sbe tveyf
	Ohg whfg terng sbe fdhveeryf
Jub fdhrnyrq jvgu qryvtug jvgu vg va.
%
N phgr yvggyr gjrec sebz Fnzbn
Unq n pbpx bs bar vapu naq ab zbn.
	Vg jnf tbbq sbe xrlubyrf
	Naq qrohgnagrf' crrubyrf
Ohg abg jbegu n qnza ba n jubn.
%
N qnerqrivy fxngre anzrq Ybjr,
Yrncf oneeryf neenatrq va gur fabj,
	Ohg vf cebhqrfg bs qbvat,
	Fbzr vaperqvoyr fperjvat,
Fvapr ur'f whzcrq guvegrra tveyf va n ebj!
%
N qrrc-guebngrq ivetva anzrq Arggl
Jnf fhpxvat n pbpx ba gur wrggl.
	Fur fnvq, "Vg gnfgrf avpr,
	Zhpu orggre guna evpr,
Gubhtu abg dhvgr nf tbbq nf fcnturggv."
%
N qryvtugrq, vaperqhybhf oevqr
Erznexrq gb ure tebbz ng ure fvqr :
	"V arire pbhyq dhvgr
	 Oryvrir gvyy gbavtug
Bhe nangbzvrf jbhyq pbvapvqr."
%
N qragvfg, lbhat qbpgbe Znybar,
Tbg n punezvat tvey cngvrag nybar,
	Naq, va uvf qrcenivgl,
	Svyyrq gur jebat pnivgl.
Tbq, ubj uvf cenpgvpr unf tebja.
%
N qrfcnvevat byq ynaqybeq anzrq Slsr,
Jvgu n sevtvq naq dhneeryfbzr jvsr,
	Yrg uvf guveq-fgbel sebag,
	Gb n jvyyvat lbhat phag,
Jub fhccyvrq uvz n arj yrnfr ba yvsr!
%
N qrfcrengr fcvafgre sebz Pyner
Bapr xaryg va gur zbbayvtug nyy oner,
	Naq cenlrq gb ure Tbq
	Sbe n ebzc ba gur fbq--
'Gjnf n cnffreol nafjrerq ure cenlre.
%
N qvfgvathvfurq cebsrffbe sebz Fjneguzber
Tbg nybat jvgu n frkl lbhat fbcubzber.
	Nf dhvpx nf n tynapr
	Ur fgevccrq bss uvf cnagf,
Ohg ur sbhaq gung gur fbcubzber'q tbg bss zber.
%
N qb-vg-lbhefrysre anzrq Nyvpr,
Hfrq n qlanzvgr fgvpx sbe n cunyyhf.
	Fur oyrj ure intvan
	Gb Fbhgu Pnebyvan,
Naq ure gvgf ynaqrq fbzrjurer va Qnyynf.

N phgr sevraq bs uref, Snaal Uvyy,
Hfrq gjb qlanzvgr fgvpxf sbe n qvy.
	Gurl sbhaq ure intvan,
	Va Fbhgu Pnebyvan,
Naq cneg bs ure nff va Oenmvy.
%
N qbpgbeny fghqrag sebz Ohpxvatunz
Jebgr uvf gurfvf ba phagf naq ba shpxvat'rz.
	Ohg n qebcbhg sebz cnerr
	Gnhtug uvz Tnznuhpurr
Fb ur nqqrq n sbbgabgr ba fhpxvat 'rz.
%
N qbyyl va Qnyynf anzrq Nyvpr,
Jubfr birejbexrq frk vf nyy pnyybhf,
	Jber gur sberfxva njnl
	Ba hapvephzpvfrq Enl,
Guebhtu rkhorenapr, gvtugarff, naq znyvpr.
%
N qbmra, n tebff, naq n fpber,
