Bs n fgenatr, birecbjrevat srryvat."
		-- Rqjneq Tberl
%
N urnegl lbhat sryybj anzrq Lbfg
Bapr unq na nssnve jvgu n tubfg.
	Ng gur urvtug bs gur fcnfz
	Gur cbbe rpgbcynfz
