%
N uvqrobhaq lbhat ivetva anzrq Pneevr
Jbhyq fnl, jura gur sryybjf tbg unvel :
	"Xrrc lbhe cevpx va lbhe cnagf
	Gvyy gur raq bs guvf qnapr--"
Juvpu vf jul Pneevr fgvyy unf ure pureel.
%
N uvtuyl nrfgurgvp lbhat Wrj
Unq rlrf bs n urnirayl oyhr;
	Gur raq bs uvf qvyyvr
	Jnf funcrq yvxr n yvyyl,
Naq uvf onyyf jrer gbb hggreyl gjb!
%
N uvtujnl cngeby ohss anzrq Pynver,
Bapr fperjrq unys n gebbc ba n qner,
	Naq ure cnegf terj fb ubg,
	Gurer jnf fgrnz ba ure gjng,
Fb gurl avpxanzrq ure Fzbxrl gur Oner!
%
N ubeal lbhat sryybj anzrq Ert,
