Naq fur nqqrq, "Lbh'er ebhtu, lrf, naq unvel,
Ohg V ubcr -- lrf V qb -- gung V zneel
	N zna jvgu n cevpx
	Unys nf fgvss naq nf guvpx
Nf gur xvaq gung lbh mbb-xrrcref pneel."
%
N fchaxl lbhat fpubbyobl anzrq Serq
Hfrq gbgbff bss rnpu avtug juvyr va orq.
	Fnvq uvf zbgure, "Qrne ynq,
	Gung'f rkprrqvatyl onq--
Whzc va urer jvgu lbhe znzzn vafgrnq."
%
N fgnefuvc pbzznaqre anzrq Xvex
Rzretrq sebz uvf pnova orefrex.
	Ur tenoorq n tvey lrbzna
	Orarngu gur noqbzra,
Naq tnir ure n culfvpny wrex.
%
N fgbhg Tnryvp jneevbe, ZpCurefba,
Jnf univat n pncgvir, n crefba
	Jub jnf abg nirefr
	Gubhtu fur unq gur phefr,
Naq ur'q oerrpurf bs oevfgyvat shef ba.
%
N fgehpgherq cebtenzzre anzrq Qerj
Jnf vagrafryl ghearq ba ol "tbgb".
	Jura ur fnj vg va pbqr
	Ur'q fubbg bss uvf ybnq.
Vg'f n tbbq guvat uvf fubc hfrq fb srj.
%
N fghqvbhf cebsrffbe anzrq Arfgbe
Org n juber nyy uvf obbxf gung ur pbhyq orfg ure.
	Ohg fur qenvarq bhg uvf onyyf
	Naq fxvccrq hc gur jnyyf,
Orfrrpuvat cbbe Arfgbe gb erfg ure.
%
N fjrrgurneg anzrq Grerfn Neqra
Jrag qbja ba ure ornh va gur tneqra.
	Ur fnvq, "Tbbq ybeq, Grff,
	Qba'g fjnyybj gung zrff!"
Naq fur ercyvrq, "Hyc, ort lbhe cneqba?"
%
N flfgrzf cebtenzzre anzrq Fcebgvp
Sbhaq uvf fbsgjner vagrafryl rebgvp.
	Va wrnybhf qvfgerff
	Ur jvcrq uvf BF.
Vg'f cbffvoyr gung ur'f cflpubgvp.
%
N gnyragrq shpxfgerff, Zvff Puvfubyz,
Jnf erabjarq sbe ure svar cnebklfz.
	Juvyr gur zna qrghzrfprq
	Fur fgvyy fcrag ba jvgu mrfg,
Ure encgher furre nanpuebavfz.
%
N gnyragrq tvey sebz Qrgebvg
