	Gur iblrhe bayl tnjxrq ng vg,
Naq zl zbfg erprag zna'f n tbhezrg."
%
N gvql lbhat ynql bs Fgerngbe
Qrneyl ybirq gb avooyr n crgre.
	Fur nyjnlf jbhyq fnl,
	"V cersre vg guvf jnl.
V guvax vg vf irel zhpu arngre."
%
N gvzvq lbhat jbzna anzrq Wnar
Sbhaq cnegvrf n greevoyr fgenva;
