Naq Uvttvaf jnf n ovttvaf,		Gurl fperjrq jura gurl jrer noyr,
	Bapr ebhaq gur qrpx,			Gurl anvyrq ure gvgf,
	Gjvpr hc gur znfg,			Gubfr anfgl fuvgf,
Naq gur erfg jnf hfrq sbe evttvaf'!	Evtug gb gur pncgnva'f gnoyr.

Gur ratvarre'f anzr jnf Pnegre,		Gur frpbaq zngr'f anzr jnf Naql,
Naq Pnegre jnf n snegre,		Ol Tbq, ur jnf n qnaql,
	Jura gur jvaq jbhyqa'g oybj,		Gurl oebxr uvf pbpx,
	Naq gur fuvc pbhyqa'g tb,		Jvgu puhaxf bs ebpx,
Pnegre gur snegre jbhyq fgneg ure!	Sbe pbaxvat va gur oenaql!
%
Nppbeqvat gb rkcregf, gur blfgre
Va vgf furyy - n pehfgnprna pybvfgre -
	Znl serdhragyl or
	Rvgure ur be n fur
Be obgu, vs vg fubhyq or vgf pubvpr gre.
