		-- Rqjneq Tberl
%
Na vadhvfvgvir ivetva anzrq Qben
Nfxrq gur zna jub fgnegrq gb ober 're :
	"Qb lbh zrna oveqf naq orrf
	Tb guebhtu nagvpf yvxr gurfr,
Gb fhccl hf bhe snhan naq syben?"
%
Na vengr lbhat ynql anzrq Obbxre
Gbyq ure uhfonaq, "Lbh ornfg, V'z ab ubbxre!
	Vs lbh jnag vg dhrre jnlf,
	Tb gb juberf sbe lbhe ynlf!"
Fb ur cnpxrq hc uvf gbby naq sbefbbx 're.
%
Na bpgntrarevna Wrj
