	Guvf jnf abg sebz pbzchapgvba,
	Ohg qhr gb qlfshapgvba
Bs uvf fcrezngvp tynaqf -- ahgf gb lbh.
%
Na byq pbhcyr whfg ng Fuebirgvqr
Jrer univat n cvrpr -- jura ur qvrq.
	Gur jvsr sbe n jrrx
	Fng gvtug ba uvf crnx,
Naq obhaprq hc naq qbja nf fur pevrq.
