Uvf ubyvarff zhezherq, "Thg lbagvss."
%
Ng n pbagrfg sbe snegvat va Ohggr
Bar ynql'f rkregvba jnf phgr :
	Vg jba gur qvcybzn
	Sbe srgvq nebzn,
Naq guerr whqtrf jrer sryyrq ol gur oehgr.
%
Ng n qnapr, n tvey sebz Pbaarpgvphg
