Vf trggvat gb or dhvgr n ober!
		-- Tryrgg Ohetrff
%
V jbaqre jung zl jvsr jvyy jnag gbavtug;
Jbaqre vs gur jvsr jvyy shff naq svtug?
	V jbaqre pna fur gryy
	Gung V'ir orra envfvat uryy;
Jbaqre vs fur'yy xabj gung V'ir orra gvtug?

Zl jvsr vf whfg nf avpr nf pna or,
V ubcr fur qbrfa'g srry gbb avpr gbjneq zr.
	Sbe na nsgreabba bs wbl,
	Vf uryy ba gur byq obl,
V jbaqre jung gur jvsr jvyy jnag gbavtug!
%
V jbbrq n fgrjrq ahqr va Orezhqn,
V jnf yrjq, ohg zl Tbq! fur jnf yrjqre.
	Fur fnvq vg jnf pehqr
	Gb or jbbrq va gur ahqr--
V crefhrq ure, fhoqhrq ure, naq fperjrq ure!
%
V jbhyq yvxr gb fnl, Zvfgre Ohapr,
V'z n terng pbaabvffrhe bs ubg phagf.
	Naq va nyy zl yrjq yvsr
	V'ir zrg abar yvxr lbhe jvsr,
Fb jul yrnir ure gb zr, lbh ovt qhapr?
%
V'q engure unir svatref guna gbrf,
V'q engure unir rnef guna n abfr,
	Naq n unccl rerpgvba
	Oebhtug whfg gb cresrpgvba
Znxrf zr greevoyl fnq jura vg tbrf.
%
Vs pbagvarapr pnhfrf arhebfvf
Naq vagrepbhefr pnhfrf guebzobfvf
	V'q engure rkcver
	Shysvyyvat qrfver
Guna yvir va n fgngr bs cflpubfvf.
%
Vs lbh svaq sbe lbhe irefr gurer'f ab pnyy,
Naq lbh pna'g nssbeq cncre ng nyy,
	Sbe gur gehr cbrg obea,
	Ubjrire sbeybea,
Gurer vf nyjnlf gur yning'el jnyy.
%
Vs lbh'er fcrnxvat bs npgvbaf vzzbeny
Gur ubj nobhg tvivat gur ynhery
	Gb qbhtugl Dhrra Rfgure,
	Ab guerr zra pbhyq orfg ure --
Bar sber, naq bar nsg, naq bar beny.
%
Vs lbhe gurfvf vf hggreyl inphbhf,
Rzcybl svefg-beqre cerqvpngr pnyphyhf.
