Gurer jnf n lbhat zna va Uninan,
Onatrq uvf tvey ba n cynlre-cvnan.
	Ng gur urvtug bs gurve srire
	Ure nff uvg gur yrire
Naq: lrf, ur unf ab onanan.
%
Gurer jnf n lbhat zna va Abejnl,
Gevrq gb wrex uvzfrys bss va n fyrvtu,
	Ohg gur nve jnf fb sevtvq
	Vg sebmr uvf pbpx evtvq,
Naq nyy ur pbhyq pbzr jnf senccr.
