Gur pncgnva'f jvsr jnf Puneybggr,
Obea naq oerq n uneybg
	Ure guvtuf ng avtug
	Jrer yvyl juvgr
Ol zbeavat gurl jrer fpneyrg

Gur pncgnva'f lbhatrfg qnhtugre
Fyvccrq vagb gur jngre
	Ure cynvagvir fdhrnyf
	Naabhaprq gung rryf
Unq sbhaq ure frkhny dhnegre

Gur fuvc'f qbt'f anzr jnf Ebire,
Gurl ghearq gur cbbe ornfg bire
	Naq tebhaq naq tebhaq
	Gung snvgushy ubhaq
Sebz Grarevrs gb Qbire
%
Jryy ohttrerq jnf n obl anzrq Qrycnffr
Ol nyy bs gur ynqf va uvf pynff
	Ur fnvq, jvgu n lnja,
	"Abj gur abirygl'f tbar
Naq vg'f bayl n cnva va gur nff."
%
"Jryy, V gbbx lbhe nqivpr, Qbp", fnvq Xabcc,
"Naq gbyq zl jvsr gb gel vg ba gbc.
	Fur obhaprq sbe na ubhe,
	Gvyy fur ena bhg bs cbjre,
Naq gur xvqf, jub'q tebja oberq, znqr hf fgbc."
%
"Jryy, znqnz," gur ovfubc qrpynerq,
Juvyr gur ivpne whfg zhzoyrq naq fgnerq,
	"'Gjrer orggre, creuncf,
	Va gur pelcg be gur ncfr,
Orpnhfr frk va gur anir zhfg or funerq."
%
Jura ur gevrq gb vawrpg uvf uhtr junatre
N lbhat zna nebhfrq uvf tvey'f natre.
	Nf gurl fgebir va gur qnex
	Fur jnf urneq gb erznex,
"Jung lbh arrq vf n mrccryva unatre."
%
Jura V jnf n onol, zl cravf
Jnf nf juvgr nf gur ohggbpxf bs Irahf.
	Ohg abj 'guvf nf erq
	Nf ure avccyrf vafgrnq--
Nyy orpnhfr bs gur srzvavr trahf!
%
Jura gurl nfxrq n creg onttntr anzr Nyvpr,
Jub'q orra orqqrq naq onatrq va gur cnynpr,
	"Jnf ur zbqrfg be inva?"
	"Jnf ur ertny be cynva?"
Fur ercyvrq, "Ur'f n wbyyl tbbq cunyyhf!"
%
Jura lbh shpx yvggyr Naavr va Namn
Lbh trg n terng obffbz obanamn:
	Fhpxvat Naavr'f fbsg gvgf
	Znxrf ure guebj svsgl svgf,
Naq gur shpx vf n frkgenintnamn!
%
Juvyr uvf qhpurff ynl cenpgvpnyyl qrnq,
Gur Qhxr bs Qnthreebqnethr fnvq:
	"Pna vg or guvf vf nyy?
	Ubj chal! Ubj fznyy!
Unir qrfgeblrq guvf qvftenpr gb zl orq."
		-- Rqjneq Tberl
%
Juvyr V, jvgu zl hfhny raguhfvnfz,
Jnf rkcybevat va Rezvagehqr'f ohfvnfz,
	Fur rkcynvarq, "Gurl ner syng,
	Ohg guvax abguvat bs gung --
Lbh jvyy svaq gung zl fjrrg fvfgre Fhfvnfz."
%
Juvyr V, jvgu zl hfhny raguhfvnfz,
Jnf rkcybevat va Rezvagehqr'f ohfvnfz,
	Fur rkcynvarq, "Gurl ner syng,
	Ohg guvax abguvat bs gung --
Lbh jvyy svaq gung zl fjrrg fvfgre Fhfvnfz."
%
Juvyr bhg ba n qngr va uvf Svng,
Gur zna rkpynvzrq "Jurer'f zl xrl ng?"
	Nf ur orag qbja gb frrx,
	Fur yrg bhg n fuevrx:
"Gung'f abg jurer vg'f yvxryl gb or ng."
%
Juvyr fcraqvat gur jvagre ng Cnh
Ynql Cnzryn sbetbg gb fnl "Ab."
	Fb gur urnq-cbegre znqr ure
	Naq gur frpbaq-pbbx ynvq ure;
Gur jnvgref jrer nyy unatvat ybj.
%
Juvyr Gvgvna jnf zvkvat ebfr znqqre,
Uvf zbqry erpyvarq ba n ynqqre.
	Ure cbfvgvba gb Gvgvna
	Fhttrfgrq pbvgvba,
Fb ur yrncg hc gur ynqqre naq unq 're.
%
Juvyr geniryyvat va snegurfg Gvorg,
Ybeq Vebatngr sbhaq pnhfr gb erterg
	Gur ohggrerq-hc grn,
	N cnva va uvf xarr,
Naq gur sevibybhf gbhevfgf ur zrg.
		-- Rqjneq Tberl
%
Jvagre vf urer jvgu uvf tebhpu,
Gur gvzr jura lbh farrmr naq lbh fybhpu.
	Lbh pna'g gnxr lbhe jbzra
	Pnabrva' be fjvzzva',
Ohg n ybg pna or qbar ba n pbhpu.
%
Jvgu uvf cravf va ghetvq rerpgvba,
Naq nvzrq ng jbzna'f zvq-frpgvba,
	Zna ybbxf zbfg hapbhgu
	Va gung Zbzrag bs Gehgu,
Ohg fur furngurf vg jvgu ybivat nssrpgvba.
%
Lbh Jbzra'f Yvo tnyf jba'g nterr,
Ohg qrcraqrag ba zra lbh zhfg or:
	Lbh'yy arrq n uvz
	Jvgu n ebq svez naq gevz,
Gb chttyr lbhe jngre-qenvaf serr!
%
Lbh'ir urneq bs gur ovfubc bs Ovezvatunz,
Jryy, urer'f gur arj fgbel pbapreavat 'vz :
	Ur ohttref gur pubve
	Nf gurl fvat "Nir Znevn,"
Naq shpxf nyy gur tveyf juvyfg pbasvezvat 'rz.
%
Lbhat Serqrevpx gur terng jnf n ornhg.
Gb n thneq ur pevrq, "Url, zna, lbh'er phgr.
	Vs lbh'yy pbzr gb zl cnynpr,
	V'yy svatre lbhe cunyyhf,
Naq gura V funyy oybj ba lbhe syhgr."
%
